**Master in City Planning, Massachusetts Institute of Technology** (2018)

**Certificate in Sustainability, MIT Sloan School of Management** (2018)

**Bachelor of Science in Civil Engineering (minor in Architecture), Columbia University** (2013)


## Professional Experience 
