* EDF Climate Corp Fellow, New York City Housing Authority (NYCHA), New York, NY (2018)
* Graduate Researchers, Special Interest Group in Urban Settlements (MIT), Cambridge, MA (2016-17)
* Assistant Manager, Mahindra Lifespaces, Mumbai, India (2013-15)


